#. i18n: ectx: (Loaded from Beta distribution calculator) <summary>
#: rkward/plugins/distributions/beta.rkh:11
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Provides a calculator for probabilities, quantiles, and densities in the "
"Beta distribution."
msgstr ""
