#, kde-format
msgid ""
"These many samples (nAvg) are used to calculate sample average. For a fixed "
"value of the parameters, one would be interested in seeing how the "
"distribution of the sample averages change as this number increases."
msgstr ""
"Úsáidtear an líon mór samplaí seo (nAvg) chun meán an tsampla a ríomh. I "
"gcás luach seasta de na paraiméadair, bheadh suim ag duine a fheiceáil conas "
"a athraíonn dáileadh na meán samplach de réir mar a mhéadaíonn an uimhir seo."

